1711:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * 						  \b Range: @ref XMC_USIC_CH_TXFIFO_INTERRUPT_NODE_POINTER_STANDARD,
1712:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * 						  			@ref XMC_USIC_CH_TXFIFO_INTERRUPT_NODE_POINTER_ALTERNATE
1713:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * @param service_request The service request to be used for interrupt generation. \n
1714:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * 						  \b Range: 0 to 5.
