 373:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * @param  oversampling Required oversampling. The value indicates the number of time quanta for on
